pageContext.claim: “If you look at the Hispanic -- very interesting, they did a Hispanic population poll, and I was at 77 percent.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is citing a nonscientific website poll hosted by Spanish-language news service Telemundo – which anyone could click. So it's totally worthless as a poll. A real Telemundo poll, conducted in September showed Joe Biden polled at 62 per cent with Latinos.
